<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Data Deletion Request - Carbon Cube Kenya</title>
  </head>

  <body style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; background-color: #f9fafb; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
    <div style="max-width: 620px; margin: 30px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
      <div style="background: #dc2626; color: #fff; text-align: center; padding: 25px 20px;">
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 10px; width: 100%;">
          <div style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle;">
            <img src="https://carboncube-ke.com/logo.png" alt="Carbon Cube Kenya" style="height: 50px; vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 8px;" />
            <span style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; letter-spacing: 1px; vertical-align: middle;">CARBONCUBE</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #fecaca;">Data Deletion Request Alert</p>
      </div>
      
      <div style="padding: 30px 25px;">
        <h1 style="color: #111827; margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 24px;">New Data Deletion Request</h1>

        <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;">A user has requested deletion of their personal data from Carbon Cube Kenya:</p>

        <div style="background: #f9fafb; padding: 18px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; font-size: 15px; color: #374151;">
          <h3 style="margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #111827; text-align: left;">User Details</h3>
          <p><strong>Name:</strong> <span style="color: #dc2626; font-weight: 600;"><%= @name %></span></p>
          <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:<%= @email %>" style="color: #dc2626; text-decoration: none;"><%= @email %></a></p>
          <% if @phone.present? %>
            <p><strong>Phone:</strong> <%= @phone %></p>
          <% end %>
          <p><strong>Account Type:</strong> <span style="color: #dc2626; font-weight: 600; text-transform: capitalize;"><%= @account_type %></span></p>
          <p><strong>Requested:</strong> <%= @timestamp %></p>
          <p><strong>Token:</strong> <code style="background: #e5e7eb; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 12px;"><%= @token %></code></p>
        </div>

        <% if @reason.present? %>
          <div style="background: #f9fafb; padding: 18px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; font-size: 15px; color: #374151;">
            <h3 style="margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #111827; text-align: left;">Reason for Deletion</h3>
            <div style="background: #ffffff; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 10px 0; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
              <p style="white-space: pre-wrap; margin: 0; line-height: 1.6; color: #374151;"><%= @reason %></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% end %>

        <div style="background: #fef2f2; border: 1px solid #fecaca; padding: 18px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
          <h3 style="margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #dc2626; text-align: left;">⚠️ Action Required</h3>
          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #991b1b;">
            This request must be processed within 30 days according to the Kenya Data Protection Act, 2019. 
            Please verify the user's identity and process the deletion request promptly.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
          <a href="mailto:<%= @email %>?subject=Re: Data Deletion Request - Verification Required" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background: #dc2626; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px; margin-right: 10px;">Contact User</a>
          <a href="https://carboncube-ke.com/admin/data-deletion-requests" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background: #6b7280; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px;">View in Admin Panel</a>
        </div>

        <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; margin: 30px 0;">
        <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">
          This is an automated notification for a data deletion request submitted through the Carbon Cube Kenya website.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div style="background: #f9fafb; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;">
        <div style="margin-bottom: 15px;">
          <img src="https://carboncube-ke.com/logo.png" alt="Carbon Cube Kenya" style="height: 25px; width: 25px; opacity: 0.7;" />
        </div>
        <p><strong>Carbon Cube Kenya</strong> | 9th Floor, CMS Africa, Nairobi</p>
        <p>Phone: +254 712 990 524 | Email: <%= ENV['BREVO_EMAIL'] %></p>
        <p>© 2025 Carbon Cube Kenya. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
